      "text": "Use cases for adapter:\n\n1) Third Party API / Vendor\n2) When we need to use Legacy code in\nconnection with our Modern codebase",
      "fontSize": 30.04550442273307,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Use cases for adapter:\n\n1) Third Party API / Vendor\n2) When we need to use Legacy code in \nconnection with our Modern codebase",
