      "text": "Definition:\n\nFacade pattern provides a simplified, unified \ninterface to a set of complex subsystem.\nIt hides the complexity of the system \nand exposes only what is necessary",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Definition:\n\nFacade pattern provides a simplified, unified \ninterface to a set of complex subsystem.\nIt hides the complexity of the system \nand exposes only what is necessary",
      "autoResize": true,
